00:00:07,260 --> 00:00:10,700
Have you ever heard about that

2
00:00:10,700 --> 00:00:13,580
the cliff of a snow mountain

3
00:00:14,100 --> 00:00:19,220
once fascinated numerous people?

4
00:00:20,900 --> 00:00:24,140
Legend has it that,

5
00:00:24,140 --> 00:00:26,940
there were treasures at the peak

6
00:00:27,780 --> 00:00:32,860
but also there was a bottomless chasm hidden over there.

7
00:00:34,460 --> 00:00:37,900
The smart, the fool

8
00:00:37,940 --> 00:00:40,740
and the kind people,

9
00:00:41,380 --> 00:00:47,220
all are familiar to you.

10
00:00:48,100 --> 00:00:51,660
On the mountainside, on the cliff,

11
00:00:51,980 --> 00:00:54,580
on the cloud,

12
00:00:54,980 --> 00:01:00,100
and in the human world,

13
00:01:11,940 --> 00:01:19,220
snowflakes are drifting profusely and disorderly.

14
00:01:30,980 --> 00:01:34,980
Joy of Life Season 1

15
00:01:34,980 --> 00:01:37,820
Episode 24

16
00:01:46,800 --> 00:01:47,680
Haven't seen you for a long time.

17
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:50,440
Madam, you're gorgeous.

18
00:01:51,550 --> 00:01:53,190
Eunuch, I'm so flattered.

19
00:01:53,720 --> 00:01:54,550
I wonder

20
00:01:54,550 --> 00:01:56,120
who want to see Xian'er today?

21
00:01:56,120 --> 00:01:58,000
Those who watched the princess grow up

22
00:01:58,310 --> 00:02:00,680
all want to see Mr. Fan.

23
00:02:01,270 --> 00:02:02,510
The Empress Dowager

24
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:04,190
also wants to see him.

25
00:02:04,270 --> 00:02:06,550
But she'll see him after lunch.

26
00:02:07,760 --> 00:02:08,600
Who should we visit first?

27
00:02:09,270 --> 00:02:10,190
Madam, since you're here,

28
00:02:10,440 --> 00:02:13,080
you certainly should visit Consort Yi first.

29
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:14,830
What about the empress?

30
00:02:15,080 --> 00:02:16,670
Her Majesty doesn't feel well today.

31
00:02:16,880 --> 00:02:18,080
We'd better not disturb her.

32
00:02:20,830 --> 00:02:21,800
This way, please.

33
00:02:27,190 --> 00:02:28,750
I know you've been to the Imperial Study,

34
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:30,830
but this is the real imperial harem.

35
00:02:31,360 --> 00:02:32,320
Don't look around.

36
00:02:32,550 --> 00:02:34,190
You might be accused of

37
00:02:34,190 --> 00:02:35,360
being disrespectful and discourteous.

38
00:02:36,270 --> 00:02:37,880
Madam, you know Consort Yi?

39
00:02:38,520 --> 00:02:40,000
She's my cousin.

40
00:02:40,720 --> 00:02:42,750
The imperial family has been gracious to my family.

41
00:02:43,110 --> 00:02:44,600
Then why do you marry my dad?

42
00:02:44,600 --> 00:02:45,520
For what?

43
00:02:45,800 --> 00:02:46,880
Whatever makes me happy!

44
00:02:46,880 --> 00:02:48,800
I see. For love.

45
00:02:49,390 --> 00:02:51,270
Don't be too arrogant when you see Her Highness later.

46
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:54,030
I see. I should save your face.

47
00:02:54,600 --> 00:02:56,550
Consort Yi is the birth mother of the Third Prince.

48
00:02:56,720 --> 00:02:57,670
Don't be disrespectful.

49
00:02:57,960 --> 00:02:59,550
Isn't the Crown Prince the third eldest among the princes?

50
00:02:59,830 --> 00:03:00,750
According to the tradition of our dynasty,

51
00:03:01,030 --> 00:03:02,440
the Crown Prince won't be included

52
00:03:02,440 --> 00:03:03,670
when ranking other princes.

53
00:03:04,320 --> 00:03:06,750
Though Consort Yi's son is still a kid,

54
00:03:07,030 --> 00:03:09,000
he's the Third Prince.

55
00:03:09,750 --> 00:03:10,960
That means

56
00:03:11,750 --> 00:03:13,600
the Crown Prince doesn't deserve to

57
00:03:14,030 --> 00:03:15,720
have any family or brother.

58
00:03:15,880 --> 00:03:17,000
How dare you say that?

59
00:03:19,030 --> 00:03:20,000
Madam, how long has it been

60
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:20,750
since you last saw Consort Yi?

61
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:22,800
It's been four years.

62
00:03:23,030 --> 00:03:23,720
It's so long!

63
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:25,720
After she married into the imperial family,

64
00:03:25,720 --> 00:03:27,190
we seldom see each other.

65
00:03:27,630 --> 00:03:28,960
Is Consort Yi cold by nature?

66
00:03:30,240 --> 00:03:31,520
Big and profound as the Liu family,

67
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:32,910
if we visit Consort Yi frequently,

68
00:03:33,320 --> 00:03:35,190
we might be suspected of collusion.

69
00:03:36,110 --> 00:03:36,880
In this sense,

70
00:03:37,190 --> 00:03:39,750
the palace walls actually become her cage.

71
00:03:40,670 --> 00:03:41,960
Indeed.

72
00:03:54,670 --> 00:03:56,240
How hard-hearted are you

73
00:03:56,240 --> 00:03:57,110
to leave me here

74
00:03:57,110 --> 00:03:58,190
to rot by myself.

75
00:03:58,190 --> 00:03:59,880
I actually have no one to talk to.

76
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:02,160
After all, the Liu family
is related to Your Highness by blood.

77
00:04:02,270 --> 00:04:03,700
We should avoid suspicion.

78
00:04:03,700 --> 00:04:03,800
=Consort Yi of Nanqing=
We should avoid suspicion.

79
00:04:03,800 --> 00:04:05,440
=Consort Yi of Nanqing=
You belong to the Fan family now.

80
00:04:05,440 --> 00:04:05,470
=Consort Yi of Nanqing=

81
00:04:05,470 --> 00:04:05,740
=Consort Yi of Nanqing=
Why worry about this?

82
00:04:05,740 --> 00:04:07,160
Why worry about this?

83
00:04:07,160 --> 00:04:08,520
Aren't I here today?

84
00:04:09,110 --> 00:04:10,830
Weren't it for Fan Xian's marriage

85
00:04:10,830 --> 00:04:12,190
with Wan'er,

86
00:04:12,470 --> 00:04:14,880
I wonder when could we

87
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:16,510
actually meet.

88
00:04:19,070 --> 00:04:20,480
You must be Fan Xian.

89
00:04:23,110 --> 00:04:25,550
Nephew Fan Xian pays respects to Auntie Liu.

90
00:04:27,950 --> 00:04:30,640
Mr. Fan, you should call Your Highness.

91
00:04:30,760 --> 00:04:31,950
You must be respectful.

92
00:04:34,110 --> 00:04:35,720
He's really a good lad.

93
00:04:39,790 --> 00:04:40,790
Fan Xian and others

94
00:04:41,070 --> 00:04:42,440
have arrived in Consort Yi's palace.

95
00:04:46,350 --> 00:04:47,640
Is Liu Ruyu with him?

96
00:04:47,830 --> 00:04:48,670
Yes.

97
00:04:51,200 --> 00:04:52,200
Haven't seen her for years,

98
00:04:53,070 --> 00:04:55,270
Consort Yi must be happy.

99
00:04:55,600 --> 00:04:57,320
I heard that Fan Xian called Her Highness

100
00:04:57,600 --> 00:04:58,880
Auntie Liu directly regardless of formalities.

101
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:01,110
Consort Yi smiled happily.

102
00:05:01,510 --> 00:05:02,270
She hasn't sent him away

103
00:05:02,510 --> 00:05:04,000
till now.

104
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:07,070
After seeing so many formalities,

105
00:05:07,950 --> 00:05:09,270
one would long for family affection instead.

106
00:05:10,040 --> 00:05:11,480
Fan Xian is really smart

107
00:05:12,440 --> 00:05:13,230
by calling her that.

108
00:05:14,670 --> 00:05:16,390
Who will he visit next?

109
00:05:17,040 --> 00:05:17,880
I've already asked.

110
00:05:18,350 --> 00:05:19,950
He will visit Imperial Consort Shu

111
00:05:19,950 --> 00:05:20,830
and Lady Ning successively.

112
00:05:21,350 --> 00:05:22,040
After the lunch,

113
00:05:22,230 --> 00:05:23,830
the Empress Dowager will see him.

114
00:05:26,070 --> 00:05:27,270
What about seizing the chance

115
00:05:27,670 --> 00:05:29,510
and making Fan Xian run into

116
00:05:30,230 --> 00:05:32,440
a maidservant when she's taking a bath?

117
00:05:33,440 --> 00:05:35,600
How do you like that?

118
00:05:41,640 --> 00:05:42,550
I'm kidding.

119
00:05:42,920 --> 00:05:44,880
It's too obvious. Nor is it interesting.

120
00:05:47,720 --> 00:05:48,670
Send someone to follow him.

121
00:05:49,070 --> 00:05:50,600
Tell me what he says.

122
00:06:06,200 --> 00:06:07,760
Where's the Third Prince?

123
00:06:08,040 --> 00:06:10,550
He's shy with strangers and dare not meet others.

124
00:06:11,040 --> 00:06:12,950
I really don't know what to do.

125
00:06:12,950 --> 00:06:14,110
When I was little,

126
00:06:14,110 --> 00:06:15,790
the most important thing is to play.

127
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:16,830
If I was asked to waste time

128
00:06:16,830 --> 00:06:18,230
meeting strangers,

129
00:06:18,230 --> 00:06:19,040
I wouldn't be happy, either.

130
00:06:19,390 --> 00:06:21,350
You're really honest.

131
00:06:21,830 --> 00:06:22,880
You might be

132
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:23,600
the first one

133
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:24,920
to say that.

134
00:06:25,670 --> 00:06:27,000
Auntie Liu is really perceptive!

135
00:06:27,230 --> 00:06:28,350
What a lad!

136
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:29,830
Your Highness,

137
00:06:30,270 --> 00:06:32,110
Imperial Consort Shu and Lady Ning

138
00:06:32,160 --> 00:06:33,070
are still waiting.

139
00:06:33,440 --> 00:06:34,110
After the lunch,

140
00:06:34,270 --> 00:06:36,670
the Empress Dowager also wants to see Mr. Fan.

141
00:06:40,160 --> 00:06:40,880
Auntie Liu,

142
00:06:41,640 --> 00:06:42,720
perhaps I should go over first.

143
00:06:42,950 --> 00:06:44,040
We are relatives.

144
00:06:44,200 --> 00:06:45,320
I'll visit you often in future.

145
00:06:45,550 --> 00:06:46,440
Go ahead.

146
00:06:48,200 --> 00:06:49,070
You should stay

147
00:06:49,070 --> 00:06:50,040
and talk with me.

148
00:06:50,760 --> 00:06:51,760
Well...

149
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:53,670
Fan Xian is the one they want to see.

150
00:06:53,830 --> 00:06:54,640
Never mind.

151
00:06:55,760 --> 00:06:57,070
Madam, stay with Auntie Liu.

152
00:06:57,070 --> 00:06:57,920
I'll be fine.

153
00:06:58,390 --> 00:06:59,760
Ruoruo, stay here, too.

154
00:07:00,200 --> 00:07:01,640
Drink some tea and eat some snacks.

155
00:07:03,110 --> 00:07:04,600
I'll go with my brother.

156
00:07:05,440 --> 00:07:07,070
Just be careful.

157
00:07:07,070 --> 00:07:08,510
When you visit other consorts,

158
00:07:08,880 --> 00:07:10,880
don't be so frivolous.

159
00:07:10,880 --> 00:07:12,070
He's not frivolous.

160
00:07:12,230 --> 00:07:14,950
I find him sincere instead.

161
00:07:16,110 --> 00:07:17,880
You're fooled by him.

162
00:07:22,790 --> 00:07:24,440
Now, we're going to Imperial Consort Shu's palace.

163
00:07:24,720 --> 00:07:26,550
Imperial Consort Shu
is the birth mother of the Second Prince.

164
00:07:27,790 --> 00:07:29,510
The Second Prince is funny.

165
00:07:29,830 --> 00:07:31,600
I wonder what his mother would be like.

166
00:07:31,760 --> 00:07:32,640
Among all the consorts,

167
00:07:32,830 --> 00:07:34,230
Imperial Consort Shu is the most rigorous,

168
00:07:34,390 --> 00:07:35,830
but I worry about her the least.

169
00:07:35,830 --> 00:07:36,510
How so?

170
00:07:37,200 --> 00:07:38,550
She won't be a problem for you.

171
00:07:38,760 --> 00:07:39,320
Why?

172
00:07:40,200 --> 00:07:41,350
Because you're talented.

173
00:07:50,830 --> 00:07:52,760
My Lady, where's Mr. Fan?

174
00:07:53,950 --> 00:07:55,070
He's over there.

175
00:07:57,320 --> 00:07:58,720
Now I understand why

176
00:07:58,720 --> 00:07:59,550
she's called Imperial Consort Shu.
('Shu' is a homophone for 'book' in Chinese)

177
00:07:59,830 --> 00:08:00,440
What?

178
00:08:01,040 --> 00:08:01,640
Nothing.

179
00:08:02,480 --> 00:08:03,230
Mr. Fan,

180
00:08:03,350 --> 00:08:04,230
take a seat, please.

181
00:08:04,550 --> 00:08:06,230
Imperial Consort Shu will be here soon.

182
00:08:14,480 --> 00:08:15,760
Your Highness!

183
00:08:15,780 --> 00:08:16,070
=Imperial Consort Shu of Nanqing=

184
00:08:16,070 --> 00:08:17,230
=Imperial Consort Shu of Nanqing=
Fan Xian is here.

185
00:08:17,230 --> 00:08:17,860
=Imperial Consort Shu of Nanqing=

186
00:08:41,640 --> 00:08:42,440
Take a seat.

187
00:08:54,910 --> 00:08:56,520
Put this book on the second layer of

188
00:08:56,520 --> 00:08:59,110
the second bookshelf on the left.

189
00:09:08,520 --> 00:09:10,000
Your poem is good.

190
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:14,110
A thousand miles from home,
I'm grieved at autumn's plight.

191
00:09:15,640 --> 00:09:16,840
Your Highness, I'm so flattered.

192
00:09:17,030 --> 00:09:17,960
Have you opened a bookstore?

193
00:09:18,320 --> 00:09:18,910
Yes.

194
00:09:19,110 --> 00:09:20,030
Do you have any unique copies?

195
00:09:20,320 --> 00:09:22,000
We only have novels.

196
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:23,000
No ancient books actually.

197
00:09:23,110 --> 00:09:26,000
I heard that you wrote the Red Mansions.

198
00:09:26,880 --> 00:09:27,960
Actually it was written

199
00:09:28,150 --> 00:09:29,320
by Mr. Cao.

200
00:09:29,640 --> 00:09:30,960
I read it by chance,

201
00:09:31,080 --> 00:09:31,880
and copied it.

202
00:09:31,960 --> 00:09:33,030
Who is he?

203
00:09:34,350 --> 00:09:36,230
I've been collecting essays of ancient times.

204
00:09:37,080 --> 00:09:38,400
How come I never heard of him?

205
00:09:41,080 --> 00:09:42,640
Anyway, the book is really good.

206
00:09:43,760 --> 00:09:45,400
Your Highness, I'm so flattered.

207
00:09:47,910 --> 00:09:50,470
What have you been reading recently?

208
00:09:51,550 --> 00:09:53,110
You publish the book.
I will take care of the network of shops.

209
00:09:53,110 --> 00:09:53,790
And then we split the profit 40/60.

210
00:09:53,960 --> 00:09:55,230
You get 60 and I get 40. What do you think?

211
00:09:56,280 --> 00:09:57,030
The account books.

212
00:09:57,230 --> 00:09:58,520
Business.

213
00:10:00,520 --> 00:10:02,400
It's vulgar after all.

214
00:10:03,400 --> 00:10:05,280
Your Highness, you're absolutely right.

215
00:10:07,400 --> 00:10:09,150
Wan'er grew up in the imperial palace.

216
00:10:09,760 --> 00:10:11,230
We all treat her as our daughter.

217
00:10:11,760 --> 00:10:13,320
So I have to see you.

218
00:10:14,440 --> 00:10:16,110
Chengze also speaks highly of you.

219
00:10:16,760 --> 00:10:18,030
Who's Chengze?

220
00:10:23,030 --> 00:10:24,440
Oh, it's the Second Prince.

221
00:10:25,790 --> 00:10:28,520
My son is arrogant.

222
00:10:28,760 --> 00:10:29,790
He seldom

223
00:10:31,150 --> 00:10:31,960
praises others.

224
00:10:32,280 --> 00:10:33,790
His Highness and I kind of hit it off

225
00:10:33,790 --> 00:10:34,640
when we first met.

226
00:10:35,350 --> 00:10:36,840
You're probably fooled by him.

227
00:10:37,840 --> 00:10:38,880
He's shrewd and deep.

228
00:10:40,320 --> 00:10:42,200
He never hits it off with others at first meeting.

229
00:10:46,230 --> 00:10:49,000
I will say no more about him.

230
00:10:50,320 --> 00:10:51,790
You'll see

231
00:10:52,710 --> 00:10:54,350
after knowing him for a long time.

232
00:10:56,710 --> 00:10:57,280
There's one thing

233
00:10:57,280 --> 00:10:58,590
you probably don't know.

234
00:10:59,760 --> 00:11:00,910
I

235
00:11:02,320 --> 00:11:03,470
love reading.

236
00:11:06,910 --> 00:11:07,710
I know. I know.

237
00:11:07,840 --> 00:11:09,400
I already know that.

238
00:11:10,110 --> 00:11:11,150
You're a younger member of the family.

239
00:11:11,710 --> 00:11:12,710
I should give you presents

240
00:11:13,150 --> 00:11:14,790
for your visit.

241
00:11:15,440 --> 00:11:17,080
I'm never fond of vulgar things.

242
00:11:17,280 --> 00:11:20,150
So I'll give you some ancient books and unique copies.

243
00:11:20,150 --> 00:11:21,590
But I don't know what you like.

244
00:11:21,590 --> 00:11:22,280
Actually, I...

245
00:11:22,590 --> 00:11:23,760
Yet, even if you tell me what you want,

246
00:11:23,760 --> 00:11:25,790
I might be unwilling to give them to you.

247
00:11:27,030 --> 00:11:28,000
Just let me pick some books

248
00:11:28,710 --> 00:11:30,350
for you.

249
00:11:33,880 --> 00:11:34,590
That's fine.

250
00:11:35,440 --> 00:11:36,880
It won't be convenient for you to hold the books.

251
00:11:37,030 --> 00:11:39,000
I'll have them sent to Consort Yi's palace.

252
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:41,910
Take them when you leave. OK?

253
00:11:42,280 --> 00:11:43,590
Your Highness, you're so considerate.

254
00:11:59,880 --> 00:12:01,150
Do you have anything else?

255
00:12:03,640 --> 00:12:04,520
Well. Well. Well.

256
00:12:04,520 --> 00:12:05,710
Then I'll see myself out.

257
00:12:12,470 --> 00:12:13,150
This way.

258
00:12:13,150 --> 00:12:14,320
OK. OK.

259
00:12:20,910 --> 00:12:21,710
I didn't expect that

260
00:12:21,910 --> 00:12:23,110
Her Highness is so different from

261
00:12:23,110 --> 00:12:23,880
the Second Prince.

262
00:12:23,880 --> 00:12:25,230
Imperial Consort Shu is quietly elegant.

263
00:12:25,230 --> 00:12:26,320
She doesn't talk much.

264
00:12:26,640 --> 00:12:27,910
She only talks to you

265
00:12:27,910 --> 00:12:29,400
because you're known as being talented.

266
00:12:29,790 --> 00:12:30,760
I really couldn't keep up with

267
00:12:30,760 --> 00:12:31,910
her sudden change of topic.

268
00:12:32,350 --> 00:12:33,840
Next, we'll visit Lady Ning,

269
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:35,150
the birth mother of the First Prince.

270
00:12:35,880 --> 00:12:37,670
By leading troops in the frontier fortress,

271
00:12:37,760 --> 00:12:38,760
the First Prince owns the military power.

272
00:12:38,880 --> 00:12:40,200
If he wants to become the Crown Prince,

273
00:12:40,200 --> 00:12:41,350
won't he gain an upper hand?

274
00:12:43,280 --> 00:12:44,110
Eunuch, it's fine.

275
00:12:44,110 --> 00:12:45,280
No one will know if you don't tell.

276
00:12:45,550 --> 00:12:46,150
You...

277
00:12:46,150 --> 00:12:47,320
The First Prince won't do that,

278
00:12:47,760 --> 00:12:48,670
and he can't.

279
00:12:49,400 --> 00:12:50,080
Why?

280
00:12:50,440 --> 00:12:52,030
Lady Ning is from Dongyi.

