289
00:13:04,640 --> 00:13:05,200
Therefore,

290
00:13:05,350 --> 00:13:06,760
he can't inherit the throne.

291
00:13:07,470 --> 00:13:08,670
That's also why the Empress Dowager

292
00:13:08,670 --> 00:13:10,150
doesn't like Lady Ning.

293
00:13:10,440 --> 00:13:11,910
She was originally an Imperial Consort.

294
00:13:12,520 --> 00:13:13,150
Years ago,

295
00:13:13,280 --> 00:13:14,440
something happened,

296
00:13:15,110 --> 00:13:16,000
and she was deprived of her rank

297
00:13:16,000 --> 00:13:16,960
and demoted to Lady.

298
00:13:18,700 --> 00:13:19,980
The old lady is quite narrow-minded.

299
00:13:23,670 --> 00:13:25,640
Mr. Fan,

300
00:13:26,150 --> 00:13:28,760
I've not lived long enough!

301
00:13:29,080 --> 00:13:29,960
Eunuch, don't worry.

302
00:13:29,960 --> 00:13:31,440
I won't say that in front of

303
00:13:31,440 --> 00:13:32,440
the Empress Dowager.

304
00:13:32,440 --> 00:13:33,670
Mr. Fan,

305
00:13:34,520 --> 00:13:36,440
don't even think about that.

306
00:13:36,710 --> 00:13:39,280
You should mind your words all the time.

307
00:13:39,440 --> 00:13:40,280
There are so many old ladies.

308
00:13:40,280 --> 00:13:42,030
Who knows I'm talking about the Empress Dowager?

309
00:14:03,620 --> 00:14:04,670
=Lady Ning of Nanqing=

310
00:14:04,670 --> 00:14:05,220
=Lady Ning of Nanqing=
Are you Fan Xian?

311
00:14:05,220 --> 00:14:05,760
