359
00:15:42,550 --> 00:15:43,880
I haven't thought about that yet.

360
00:15:44,790 --> 00:15:45,590
No need to be nervous.

361
00:15:45,590 --> 00:15:46,470
I won't push you.

362
00:15:46,840 --> 00:15:47,840
Come one. Let's eat!

363
