406
00:17:55,190 --> 00:17:56,560
Let the Empress Dowager see you.

407
00:17:58,470 --> 00:17:59,310
Kneel down here?

408
00:17:59,680 --> 00:18:00,430
Yes.

409
00:18:01,230 --> 00:18:02,110
Without entering the palace?

410
00:18:02,470 --> 00:18:04,680
It's the Empress Dowager's order. Just kneel down.

411
00:18:05,470 --> 00:18:06,800
I've never knelt down before His Majesty.

412
00:18:08,280 --> 00:18:09,040
Just kneel down.

413
00:18:10,680 --> 00:18:11,310
Fine.

414
00:18:11,640 --> 00:18:13,110
I'm just showing respect to the old.

415
00:18:17,280 --> 00:18:20,110
The Empress Dowager only asks Mr. Fan to kneel down.

416
00:18:20,280 --> 00:18:21,190
I'll keep my brother company.

417
00:18:25,920 --> 00:18:26,830
Can Her Majesty see me

418
00:18:27,040 --> 00:18:28,280
kneeling down here?

419
00:18:33,950 --> 00:18:34,710
Who's that?

420
00:18:39,520 --> 00:18:40,520
Mind your words.

421
00:18:41,830 --> 00:18:42,880
It's Eunuch Hong.

422
00:18:48,590 --> 00:18:50,160
Who are the Four Great Masters?

423
00:18:50,560 --> 00:18:52,000
Nanqing has two Great Masters.

424
00:18:52,310 --> 00:18:54,920
One is Liuyun Palm Ye Liuyun.

425
00:18:55,310 --> 00:18:57,830
The other is mysterious and unknown.

426
00:18:59,520 --> 00:19:00,950
Rumor has it that he is hidden

427
00:19:00,950 --> 00:19:02,470
in the imperial palace of the capital city.

428
00:19:03,000 --> 00:19:03,920
There's other speculation that

429
00:19:04,560 --> 00:19:05,880
he is an old eunuch

430
00:19:05,880 --> 00:19:06,700
