00:19:06,710 --> 00:19:08,500
=Hong Sixiang, Head of Eunuchs of Nanqing=

433
00:19:13,830 --> 00:19:14,880
The Empress Dowager said

434
00:19:15,640 --> 00:19:17,710
you shouldn't kneel down for respecting the old.

435
00:19:18,950 --> 00:19:19,800
You're kneeling down here because as an official,

436
00:19:20,560 --> 00:19:22,920
you should show respect to the imperial family.

437
00:19:23,400 --> 00:19:24,350
The Empress Dowager also said

438
00:19:25,310 --> 00:19:28,520
next time you see His Majesty,
you'd better kneel down before him.

439
00:19:28,640 --> 00:19:30,230
Can she hear me inside...

440
00:19:33,070 --> 00:19:34,160
You could hear me, right?

441
00:19:35,400 --> 00:19:38,280
You'd better mind your words

442
00:19:38,950 --> 00:19:40,350
and behaviors inside the imperial palace.

443
00:19:41,000 --> 00:19:41,950
Not everyone has a good hearing

444
00:19:41,950 --> 00:19:43,350
as you do.

445
00:19:45,160 --> 00:19:46,680
The Empress Dowager asked me to tell you.

446
00:19:47,110 --> 00:19:48,430
Treat Wan'er nicely.

447
00:19:48,880 --> 00:19:50,280
If you ever make her sad,

448
00:19:51,430 --> 00:19:53,640
you'll have to die for that.

449
00:20:02,280 --> 00:20:04,040
Eunuch Hong, please tell Her Majesty that

450
00:20:04,920 --> 00:20:06,000
her words might

451
00:20:06,000 --> 00:20:07,070
have the exactly opposite effect.

452
00:20:07,800 --> 00:20:08,430
They'll keep others

453
00:20:08,430 --> 00:20:09,760
away from Wan'er instead.

454
00:20:11,190 --> 00:20:11,880
Are you scared?

455
00:20:12,160 --> 00:20:13,350
I'll treat Wan'er nicely

456
00:20:13,470 --> 00:20:15,070
because I love her wholeheartedly.

457
00:20:15,680 --> 00:20:16,520
I'll protect her

458
00:20:17,160 --> 00:20:18,920
no matter what Her Majesty said.

459
00:20:21,280 --> 00:20:24,590
I hope you can remember your own words.

460
00:20:25,680 --> 00:20:27,070
Escort him out the imperial palace.

461
00:20:37,800 --> 00:20:38,680
Eunuch Hong,

462
00:20:39,590 --> 00:20:41,590
are you a Great Master?

463
00:21:05,400 --> 00:21:07,230
That kid is unwilling to submit.

464
00:21:08,160 --> 00:21:09,110
But he said

465
00:21:09,680 --> 00:21:11,350
