473
00:21:29,070 --> 00:21:30,000
but I don't like him.

474
00:21:30,280 --> 00:21:31,070
Why?

475
00:21:31,350 --> 00:21:32,400
I can't tell.

476
00:21:36,280 --> 00:21:39,640
I just feel that

