487
00:22:07,830 --> 00:22:10,110
I'll congratulate you in advance

488
00:22:10,160 --> 00:22:11,560
for good luck and happiness.

489
00:22:16,830 --> 00:22:17,590
Well, you...

490
00:22:18,520 --> 00:22:20,640
I really mean to congratulate you.

491
00:22:20,800 --> 00:22:22,590
And I really mean to thank you.

492
00:22:23,310 --> 00:22:26,310
Then I'll take it.

493
00:22:43,190 --> 00:22:44,590
The Princess Royal wants to see Fan Xian.

494
00:22:47,160 --> 00:22:49,310
No one has told me in advance.

495
00:22:49,310 --> 00:22:50,350
Her Highness didn't want to see him then,

496
00:22:50,880 --> 00:22:51,880
but now she wants to see him.

497
00:22:51,880 --> 00:22:52,590
Well...

498
00:22:52,590 --> 00:22:54,110
I'm here for Wan'er,

499
00:22:54,640 --> 00:22:56,070
so I definitely should visit Her Highness.

500
00:22:56,400 --> 00:22:57,280
Please lead the way.

501
00:22:57,590 --> 00:22:59,190
Her Highness only wants to see you.

502
00:22:59,590 --> 00:23:00,470
They should wait for you

503
00:23:00,830 --> 00:23:02,190
in Consort Yi's palace.

504
00:23:02,590 --> 00:23:03,280
Brother.

505
00:23:05,350 --> 00:23:06,280
Please.

506
00:23:15,760 --> 00:23:16,800
What?

507
00:23:16,830 --> 00:23:18,680
The Princess Royal wants to see Fan Xian alone!

508
00:23:18,880 --> 00:23:19,950
He should visit her.

509
00:23:20,230 --> 00:23:22,110
After all, she's the birth mother of Wan'er.

510
00:23:22,400 --> 00:23:23,430
Is there anything wrong?

511
00:23:24,520 --> 00:23:25,920
The Princess Royal appears to be

512
00:23:25,920 --> 00:23:27,520
soft and delicate in the imperial palace.

513
00:23:28,400 --> 00:23:29,560
However...

514
00:23:30,000 --> 00:23:30,880
However what?

515
00:23:31,920 --> 00:23:34,040
However, if you know her for a long time,

516
00:23:34,430 --> 00:23:35,590
you'll feel there's something hidden

517
00:23:35,590 --> 00:23:36,920
under her appearance.

518
00:23:39,950 --> 00:23:40,710
What does that mean?

519
00:23:41,310 --> 00:23:42,190
It's just like

520
00:23:43,760 --> 00:23:46,590
