541
00:25:04,160 --> 00:25:04,950
Now, Wan'er is also

542
00:25:05,880 --> 00:25:07,920
getting better.

543
00:25:08,190 --> 00:25:10,160
I just happen to know some folk prescriptions.

544
00:25:12,710 --> 00:25:14,230
Do you have any folk prescription for headache?

545
00:25:15,110 --> 00:25:17,000
Headache has many causes.

546
00:25:17,000 --> 00:25:18,590
My teacher also found it a headache

547
00:25:18,590 --> 00:25:20,040
to explain them to me.

548
00:25:22,520 --> 00:25:24,310
Isn't there any good method?

549
00:25:24,640 --> 00:25:25,830
I actually learned

550
00:25:25,830 --> 00:25:26,830
massage from my teacher.

551
00:25:26,950 --> 00:25:28,520
It might relieve the pain.

552
00:25:29,950 --> 00:25:30,880
Try it on me.

553
00:25:31,400 --> 00:25:32,590
I'm afraid it's not appropriate.

554
00:25:33,110 --> 00:25:35,230
Mr. Fan, you're so old-fashioned.

555
00:25:35,800 --> 00:25:36,880
In a few days,

556
00:25:37,520 --> 00:25:38,880
you'll become my son-in-law.

557
00:25:39,400 --> 00:25:40,280
What are you afraid of?

558
00:25:42,000 --> 00:25:43,190
I'll certainly obey the order

559
00:25:43,640 --> 00:25:44,520
from the elder.

560
00:25:57,920 --> 00:25:59,280
Have you started?

561
00:26:11,310 --> 00:26:12,760
Have you also learned the technique

562
00:26:13,190 --> 00:26:14,800
from Fei Jie?

563
00:26:15,310 --> 00:26:17,110
The acupoint recognition method
is also taught by my teacher.

564
00:26:19,470 --> 00:26:21,110
I do feel much relieved.

